    v2 = wp.cos(wp.abs(wp.abs(v0 + 0.56)))
    v0 = ((0.68 + (tmp + 0.43 + v0 + 0.60)) + wp.exp((v0 + 0.14 / tmp + 0.98)))
    v1 = (wp.abs(v0) + wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.08)))
    tmp = 0.14
    v1 = 0.29
